                <h1>"How to Reduce Background Noise on a Fifine Mic"</h1>
                <p>The Fifine mic is renowned for its quality, but it can pick up background noise if not configured properly. To minimize unwanted sounds, ensure you're in a quiet space, use a pop filter, and consider adjusting the gain settings. Positioning the mic closer to your mouth can also help focus on your voice while reducing ambient noise.</p>
